doSearch

public Map<Integer,Integer> doSearch(String query)
Returns a Map of airport ids and Rank to put in search results. An exact match will return a single-element Map. The rank is incremented each time the query matches search criteria, if the airport Rank is high according to the db and if the airport is in close proximity. If no match is found, return a Map with a single element with airportId -1.

Specified by:
doSearch in interface AviationDbAdapter
Parameters:
query - A string to try to match.
